author: mxmanghi
msg: Rivet_ExecuteErrorHandler. Error handling generalized and Tcl
status returned by Tcl_EvalObjEx is propagated by Rivet_ExecuteAndCheck
to interrupt execution even when an error occurs or abort_page is
called from a nested template. Flag globals->page_aborting is
used to prevent error loggin because ::rivet::abort_page is called.
Therefore globals->page_aborting is reset when a real error occurs
